Setting: Day, bright, heat, sand, urban

Objective: Bomb

Description: In a bombed out middle eastern environment the terrorists are trying 
to take back control over the city, their objective; destroy the military checkpoints.
Civilians abandoned the area when war broke out, the only thing remaining is the 
terrorists safe houses.
The area is considered to dangerous for regular military personnel, a small special 
unit of elite forces has been assigned to deal with the hostile threat.
